:Theme_DeathAndHadesReverence a :Theme,
        owl:NamedIndividual ;
    :description "The logic of death: appeal to Hades and the futility or cost of revering the underworld."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_ErosOverpowersReasonAndLaw a :Theme,
        owl:NamedIndividual ;
    :description "Eros as an irresistible force that subverts reason, justice, and social order."^^xsd:string .

